headline: Franklin Templeton Canada Announces Estimated December ETF Cash Distributions and Annual Reinvested Distributions
summary: Franklin Templeton Canada today announced the estimated December 2024 cash distributions and the annual reinvested distributions for its ETFs and ETF series of mutual funds available to Canadian investors.

headline: SEC Approves First Spot Bitcoin and Ethereum Combo ETFs
summary: The U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) has approved the first crypto index exchange-traded funds (ETFs) from Hashdex and Franklin Templeton.
